welcome_message_body: "Welcome to charming Camano, where breathtaking nature and small-town charm await you. Known for its stunning beaches and vibrant art scene, we invite you to explore and experience all that this beautiful city has to offer. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Snohomish County - Paine Field Airport houses all of the necessary facilities for passengers, including check-in counters, security checkpoints, and baggage claim.
